{"type":null,"faqId":38462,"title":"拍摄照片","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.41527778in;}\n.p1{text-indent:-0.110416666in;margin-left:1.18125in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{margin-bottom:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:9pt;}\n.p3{margin-left:1.4409722in;margin-top:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:9pt;}\n.p4{text-indent:0.19305556in;margin-left:0.09861111in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">1.  </span><span>在主屏幕，点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=125230\" style=\"width:0.24305555in;height:0.1875in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”“相机”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">2.  </span><span>将镜头对准要拍摄的对象，相机将自动对焦。也可以点击屏幕对某个点进行对焦。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=125231\" style=\"width:0.5in;height:0.16597222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<span>若对焦框变为红色，表示对焦失败，请重新对焦。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=125232\" style=\"width:0.5in;height:0.16597222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<span>若在拍摄照片时开启了“地理位置”开关，所拍照片可通过“图库”的“地图”模式进行浏览。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\"></p>\n<p class=\"p4\"></p>\n<p class=\"p4\"></p>\n<p class=\"p4\"></p>\n<p class=\"p4\"></p>\n<p class=\"p4\"></p>\n<p class=\"p4\"></p>\n<p class=\"p4\"></p>\n<p class=\"p4\"></p>\n<p class=\"p4\"></p>\n<p class=\"p4\"></p>\n</div>\n</bo